title: Alanis's Daily Routine
description: Alanis Daily Routine is a true story about a sweet girl name Alanis D. Newell who is now thirteen years old anduuuuuuuuu she suffers with Autism. Her story tells how she deals with her challenges on a day to day routine. Alanis expresses her emotions and how she has overcome many obstacles while accomplishing her goals.
author: Trauma Fontaine Newell
